<h2>Code</h2>
<p>Code samples should be wrapped in the <code>&lt;code&gt;</code> element (as the text "&lt;code&gt;" just was). Code samples spanning multiple lines should have their whitespace preserved for readability, which can be accomplished by wrapping it in <code>&lt;pre&gt;</code> tags, like this:</p>
<pre><code>function awesomize($input) {
    return $input . ' and Steve';
  }</code></pre>

